<body>
	
<header>
	Listen to Part One of an interview with Zenia. Are the following statements true or false?
</header>
	
<section id="body">
	<br/><ol id="questionList"><br/><li id="q1">The Examiner introduces herself to the candidate.<a id="1" >True</a><tab/><a id="2" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q2">Zenia has to give the Examiner her full name.<a id="3" >True</a><tab/><a id="4" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q3">Zenia does not need to produce identification.<a id="5" >True</a><tab/><a id="6" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q4">The candidate has a turn to ask questions.<a id="7" >True</a><tab/><a id="8" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q5">The candidate is asked where she comes from.<a id="9" >True</a><tab/><a id="10" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q6">The candidate asks the Examiner her name.<a id="11" >True</a><tab/><a id="12" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q7">Zenia is asked to describe her home town.<a id="13" >True</a><tab/><a id="14" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q8">The Examiner asks Zenia about her family.<a id="15" >True</a><tab/><a id="16" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q9">The candidate is asked where she was born.<a id="17" >True</a><tab/><a id="18" >False</a><br/></li><br/><li id="q10">The Examiner asks Zenia to talk about her life.<a id="19" >True</a><tab/><a id="20" >False</a><br/></li></ol><media class="leftFloat" src="../Media/Unit01_e3.flv" mode="1" id="1003"  />
</section>
<section id="fb1">
	<p align="left">1. When you give your name to someone this is an introduction.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb2">
	<p align="left">2. This is important so that the Examiner can check the candidate's identity.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb3">
	<p align="left">3. Identification is essential, you can't take the exam without it.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb4">
	<p align="left">4. The Examiner asks all the questions.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb5">
	<p align="left">5. This is one of the first questions the Examiner will ask.</p>
</section>
<section id="fb6">
	<p align="left">6. The Examiner gives her name without the candidate having to ask. </p>
</section>
<section id="fb7">
	<p align="left">7. She doesn't have to go into lots of detail but gives a short description.</p>
</section>
